The Arabic Qur'an for Arabic PC
To Install Arabic Support on Windows XP follow following steps
Control Panel - Regional and Language Options - Languages (on 2nd Page) - Suplimental Langauge Support - Install files for complex script and right to left languages
 - Press OK - It may ask for XP CD - Follow instructions and reboot if it asks. Then make Arabic as default language or select font in mIRC with Arabic Script.
Visit: http://quran.nu/ar/

